  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nBesu has implemented the Parity style Trace_Call but not the more recent Debug_TraceCall that is implemented in [Geth](https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interacting-with-geth/rpc/ns-debug#debugtracecall) and Erigon and used by infrastructure providers like Infura and Linea.\r\n\r\nAs a network participant, I would like access to this debug call in the same namespace and format as other clients so that I can drop in replace Besu in certain networks/tooling/RPC stacks. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Implementation - can be based on Geth implementation and Besu Trace_Call (with slightly different format). ",
